planning.user_prompt:
Thinking step by step, first consider the client request, refine the client request into a project description that clearly specifies the big picture goal of our research, and return a project plan as JSON {original_client_request, project_description, task_descriptions[]}. The task_descriptions should each be a string that clearly instructs one of our research analysts on what we need. Together, the completed tasks will allow us to brief the client and give them the info they seek.

Maximum Task Count: 5

Client Request: {userRequest}

research.user_prompt:
Project Description: {projectDescription}

Task: {task}

OUTPUT FORMAT: Always perform thorough and diligent research to back up your statements. Always provide links to your sources as plaintext at the end of your response like [Article Title(url)]
